 Stat Talk Slums 

 According to UN-Habitat rsquo;s Global Report on Human Settlements 2003, the Calcutta Municipal Corporation area has more than 5,000 slums, registered and unregistered. One out of three Calcuttans lives in a slum. In some wards, more than 90 per cent of the population live in slums, the 2001 census report says.

